PrecisRegulations Amending the LIVESTOCK AND POULTRY CARCASS GRADING REGULATIONS which increase the maximum allowable carcass weight for VEAL and the maximum graded carcass weight, make grade-stamping optional for heavier carcasses and slightly modify the muscling requirements for grades Canada A and B.

precis:
Regulations Amending the LIVESTOCK AND POULTRY CARCASS GRADING REGULATIONS
which increase the maximum allowable carcass weight for VEAL and the
maximum graded carcass weight, make grade-stamping optional for heavier
carcasses and slightly modify the muscling requirements for grades
Canada A and B.
